channel.title: The ServerConsole: HEAVY update on the ServerconsolePlayerHandler(Pictures)
channel.description:
I have updated my serverConsole :-) Updates: • MenuBar works • Adding buttons • Hooked up Serverconsole to the server • Took screenies ;P • Added stuff on the menubar • Made the function Ban/Kick work • Added a bit stuff for the server restarter (20%) • HEAVLY updated serverconsole playerhandler • ~~More To Come~~
Im making this for my server project "RuneBlaze" ○Currently working on: [b]Serverconsole playerhandler[/b] Posts are welcome!
• Equipment/Files:
[size=15pt]○ Hooked up on a server ○[/size] [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img338.imageshack.us/img338/8206/file2zp5.png[/img][/URL]
[size=15pt]○ Not hooked up on a server ○[/size] Listeners deleted but going to add again [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img300.imageshack.us/img300/2713/console1vt3.png[/img][/URL]
• When activated:
[size=15pt]○ ServerConsole itself ○[/size] Pressed some actions ;) [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img73.imageshack.us/img73/664/consoleplznw2.png[/img][/URL]
[size=15pt]○ ServerConsoled playerhandler ○[/size] Updated it heavly removed button listeners but gonna add again ;) [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img520.imageshack.us/img520/9287/5y80cw5co8.png[/img][/URL] Place: This will be a new option with booleans. I will get square coords of cities (like safezone) and give them a name Wish me luck on getting the cities, Sick wants me to do it per building lolz o.O
